text: KAJK (96.3 FM) is a radio station licensed to Susanville, California, United States. It serves Lassen County, California. The station is owned by Independence Rock Media Group, through licensee Thomas Huth Revocable Living Trust. That company is in turn partially owned by Gary Katz. ==External links== * * AJK Category:Jack FM stations Category:Radio stations established in 2005 Category:Lassen County, California
